    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted the package on the basis that all 7 assessed credibility factors demonstrated positive validation metrics and that Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was completed. The team noted that the primary validation evidence (hemolysis and velocity field results) was generated under model configuration ansys-cfx-24-build-2024q3 (modelVersion 2024-q3-build-2) and that the current model of record is 2026-q1-build-7; however, this version discrepancy was treated as a documentation gap rather than a material difference. This acceptance decision is erroneous: the supporting ValidationResults do not apply to the current model version, constituting a W-AR-04 model version drift weakener.",
